## Instructions
Analyze this meeting transcript and provide a JSON response with the following fields:
- title: meeting title
- attendees: list of attendee names
- summary: 2-3 sentence overview of the meeting
- action_items: list of objects with fields: assignee, action, related_issue (number or null), related_jira (ticket key or null), due (date string or null)
- decisions: list of decisions made during the meeting
- mentioned_issues: list of GitHub issue numbers mentioned
- mentioned_prs: list of PR numbers mentioned
- mentioned_jira_tickets: list of Jira ticket keys mentioned
- key_topics: list of main topics discussed
- confidence: 0.0 to 1.0

Respond ONLY with valid JSON. Do not include markdown formatting or code fences.